needGuildCfg: Set a channel before you do that.

help.en:
Star reaction bot
v1.0.0

`-setchannel <channelId>` - sets pin channel for this guild
`-setnsfw <channelId>` - sets nsfw channel
`-setlang <lang>` - sets language for this guild
`-help` - displays this message
